title: TheGreenPapers, New Jersey Democratic primary, New Jersey, 2008
name: TheGreenPapers, New Jersey Democratic primary, New Jersey, 2008
description: The poly shapefile was generated from the democratic Primary data scraped from the Green Papers website. It has votes and delegate counts for Clinton and Obama for the 5th Feb, 2008 primary.  The data is available for the 20 "Democratic  Districts" while the Census shape file is available for New Jersey for the 40 "Legislative Districts". Thus one "Democratic District" data is allocated to two "Legislative Districts" to generate the shape file.

author.source: The Green Papers and Census State Legislative Boundary File
